PageTitle: clock frequency enable (virtual access port-extension view)
FuncDef:
The clock frequency enable command enables frequency synchronization.
The undo clock frequency enable command disables frequency synchronization.
By default, frequency synchronization is disabled.
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
This command is used for deployment of frequency synchronization in virtual access scenarios.
Precautions
In VS mode, this command is supported only by the admin VS.
